so-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（二）机密级事项</span></font></p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">目&ldquo;战略规划和总体布局&rdquo;，包括医药生产、科研开发及</span></font></p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><font size=\"3\">流通，十年以上的战略规划和方向性国家医药总体布局。</font></span></p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">&ldquo;重大方针政策&rdquo;，指对医药事业全局的发展产生影响的方针</span></font></p><p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><font size=\"3\">政策，如为发展医药科研技术而采取的重要战略性方针政策等。</fon